paren><closeparen><space>if<space>len<openparen>s<closeparen><space>==<space>1<closebracket>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>if<space>flag<space><lt><space>0:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>line.reverse<openparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>feature.setGeometry<openparen>line<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.pyoutput<openparen>feature<closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><lf><space><space><space><space>def<space>chop<openparen>self<comma><space>surface<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>if<space>isinstance<openparen>surface<comma><space>fmeobjects.FMEFace<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.chopped<space>+=<space>surface.getAsWireFrame<openparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>elif<space>isinstance<openparen>surface<comma><space>fmeobjects.FMEMesh<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.chopped<space>+=<space>surface.getAsWireFrame<openparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>elif<space>isinstance<openparen>surface<comma><space>fmeobjects.FMERectangleFace<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>self.chop<openparen>surface.getAsFaceCopy<openparen><closeparen><closeparen><lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>elif<space>isinstance<openparen>surface<comma><space>fmeobjects.FMETriangleFan<closeparen>:<lf><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space><space>for<space>i<space>in<space>range<openparen>surface.